Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== OPCN ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我心中潛伏的PRISONER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:27.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永存於愛之名下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:42.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}歷史的夾縫中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}隱藏著無法治癒的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:57.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}人類是可悲的忘卻生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:03.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}為何人展開翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:08.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}於剎那之盡頭獻上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:14.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}較之昨日已更加成長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:20.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}美麗的側臉卻在孤獨中動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}你心中潛伏的PRISONER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}背負永不消失的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:30.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}為必須守護的世界 請別嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}若世界將你否定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:36.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我也會伴你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}僅有無法退讓的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:46.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}懷於胸中 直擊黑暗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== OPJP ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}ワタシの中に潜むPRISONER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:27.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永久に愛の名のもとに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:42.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}歴史の狭間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}癒えぬ痛みを隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:57.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}人は哀しいほど忘れる生き物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:03.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}誰がために　羽を広げ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:08.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}刹那の果て　命を捧ぐのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:14.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}昨日よりも　大人びてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:20.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}綺麗なその横顔が　孤独に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:23.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}アナタの中に潜むPRISONER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}消えない印を背負い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:30.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}護るべき正義の為に　嘆かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}もしも世界が　否定をしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:36.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}私がそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}譲れない想いだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:46.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}胸に抱いて　暗闇を撃て
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== EDCN ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:54.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算之前人生的策略使人盡失夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:00.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扣動扳機 隨著勇敢之夢繼續向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然要挑戰不存在冬季的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:05.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然要心懷無法抑制的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:07.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就做好覺悟勇往直前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:10.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脱離自我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:15.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然是奪走一切的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我該以何種信念活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:25.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然害怕局限與受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:27.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就連未來都捨棄
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== EDJP ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:29.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}OOH YEAH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:30.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They bring me DOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all the world is stereotypical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:33.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're Playing out rules
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:35.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}but act another, Look
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:36.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now you thought
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:37.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you had me by the upper － hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:40.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}but I see through the face you've covered cynical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:40.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( FOUR )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:42.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}unleash the beast to fight inside at you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.73,0:22:43.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( THREE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:45.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To calm the fire that burns in front of you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:45.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( TWO )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.65,0:22:47.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Without the fear and tears surrounding you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:48.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:50.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because your soul is what you were BORN TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:54.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たとえ今まで生きるstrategy 夢失っても　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:55.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(It's time now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ハンドルを切って暴れ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夢のまま突き進め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:03.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬のない人生に挑むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:05.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忍のない感情を抱くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:07.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覚悟決めて行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:10.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分自身をbreak away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:15.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全てを奪われる運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何を信じて生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:22.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ask yourself, the way there's nothing to live or die for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:25.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過去も傷も恐れるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.37,0:23:27.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未来さえも捨てるようなもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:30.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Choice is yours to make
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:32.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is what I choose to live for
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== MAIN ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如今尋找五十島的線索已經斷絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能依靠的 只有最後的預知夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,強忍著不願意相信的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我又回到了這個家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,武也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 在那裡我看見的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如同噩夢般的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果噩夢的話 就讓我快點醒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我從心裡如此盼望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.07,0:01:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你對媽媽做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我話說在前頭 可是她先動手的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我這算正當防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你對媽媽做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 我沒殺掉她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你閃開 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它改造過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 武啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓我試試刀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們上吧 薄暮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,夢魘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,武那可愛的寵物已經不在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊 永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,月光…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,武啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴你一個好消息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那時的凶手 其實不是武
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是三年前的那場車禍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為是你把我推出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看來也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 其實真相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是媽媽拜託卡美洛的主教 想要殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她居然為了殺我 做到那份上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 她的計劃失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我的腿受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽就不想再傷害我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,武 一切的元凶都是媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼媽媽想殺你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,關於這個 媽媽無論如何都不告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,又做了同樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,得想想辦法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓月光變成和馬那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 武
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那人真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,把罪行推到武身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還若無其事地欺騙了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是吃驚得說不出話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過那也是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我也大吃一驚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你就為了問出這種事情 而傷害了媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 說得好像我才是壞人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,武從一開始就毫不在意我的腿會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你和媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,心想著那時我要是死了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你別太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在做的事情只是找藉口傷害別人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,居然傷害了媽媽 你到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,結果我們還是不能相互理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,該做個了結了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼兄弟之間非得戰鬥不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經不是那時的月光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如永夜中降下的落雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,眼前的月光…現在的月光…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,毀滅指示已到來 如今正是成為先導者之時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,飛翔至冥府盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,墜落而下的星雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,吾之名為墮落者 飛馳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,迎擊吧 危刻冰刃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,速度變快了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,引路人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,七瀨 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,六 離遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,別想著孤身奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 一起掩護七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來當那些人的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊 小的們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就恭敬不如從命了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,武 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,伊田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,伊田 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這點小傷不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,對你來說還太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,到我們身後掩護吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會在這裡撤退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我可保證不了你能全身而退哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,停手吧 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續啊 武
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽一心想殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,反正武也不會再原諒我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒有可以去的地方了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,離開引路人 和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 武
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是有多天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 這不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,武
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島… 五十島…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島… 五十島！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,別想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,別管我 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的兄妹相似嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,六 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,武 不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃 不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,武…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,武 快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候該完結這一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,完結這一切？你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 說到底全都怪武你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為你從我這奪走了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才會成這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我說的不是嗎 武
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是你的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不要繼續戰鬥下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,兩人的力量似乎開始暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我也開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,和馬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,七瀨去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 從這開始創造屬於我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一切的命運都早已注定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,感到有點懷念嗎 和馬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,維歐 你為什麼現在還對我如此忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你過去曾拯救了我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在那時我就發誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一切都是為了你而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我已經不是那時的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你心意有所轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的決意也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你也真是好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 未來一定會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,和馬大人 該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,到那嶄新的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 我記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,五十島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,學院應該是被毀壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,來 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快點啊 在磨蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了 一氏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,千木老師別丟下我先走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一氏老師… 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託我做的宣傳手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,已經照學年區分了顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你了 一氏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼一回事 到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況 完全搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,1998年 這是什麼 到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,請放開我 鷲津學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,別說得這麼冷淡嘛 小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,鷲津？院長？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該住手了吧 吉平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 月臣想離間我和小不點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,既是和馬的好友更是得力助手的藤川月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,愛上了千木陽子 背叛了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然後為了保護陽子而死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,優等生的你在這種地方做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在找千木老師 你有看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,月臣 你憧憬的陽子老師在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,別拿我開玩笑了 和馬你也來說兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,繡眼鳥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 和馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…龍泉寺和馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我難道是穿越到了過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,吉平 和馬 月臣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,別在這偷懶了 快來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,月光 難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一點沒幹勁的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去年也是說這種話 一直都在偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,今年一定得來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:06.99,NOTE,,0,0,0,,鷲津學長 請快點住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.83,NOTE,,0,0,0,,不然就把你拋到宇宙空間去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.55,NOTE,,0,0,0,,哇 好可怕 真有點過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:17.25,NOTE,,0,0,0,,既然你這麼做的話 我就來把小不點你化掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去年？為什麼會和他們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是夢的話就快醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你好久了 武
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我有件事必須得告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,武
